Shelby Chong https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Shelby_Chong 0 Shelby Chong (née Fiddis; born February 1, 1948) is an American comedian, actress and producer who was the executive producer of Best Buds (2003) and the associate producer of four Cheech Chong films. She is the wife of comedian and actor Tommy Chong.
